## Problem
Considering $S_{\\mathrm{b}} \\simeq S_{\\mathrm{c}}$ and $S_{\\mathrm{t}} \\ll S_{\\mathrm{b}}$, determine the expressions for (1) $F_{\\mathrm{s}}^{\\star}$ and (2) $X^{\\star}$ as functions of $\\rho, g, S_{\\mathrm{c}}$ and $A$. (3) Express the corresponding maximum energy $W^{\\star}$, (4) then calculate its numerical value in $\\mathrm{mJ}$ with $A = 5 \\times 10^{2} \\mathrm{Pa}$.